---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import TechLogos from "../components/TechLogos.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import dealermadeImg from "../images/dealermade.png";
---

<Layout title="Projects — Mozek Technologies">
  <!-- ══════════ HERO ══════════ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden pb-20 pt-16 lg:pb-28 lg:pt-24">
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute left-0 top-0 h-[600px] w-[600px] -translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/4 rounded-full bg-teal/[0.06] blur-[120px]"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <h1
        class="animate-on-load max-w-2xl font-heading text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-white lg:text-6xl"
      >
        Success Stories
      </h1>
      <p
        class="animate-on-load-d1 mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-400"
      >
        Real-world engagements that demonstrate how Mozek delivers measurable
        impact through cloud, data, and AI solutions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══════════ CASE STUDY ══════════ -->
  <section class="bg-navy-light py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div
        class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-navy"
        data-animate
      >
        <!-- Client header -->
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/[0.06] px-8 py-6"
        >
          <Image
            src={dealermadeImg}
            alt="DealerMade logo"
            class="h-10 w-auto"
            height={40}
          />
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-white">
              DealerMade
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">B2B SaaS &middot; Texas</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-12 px-8 py-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr,380px]">
          <!-- Case study text -->
          <div class="space-y-5 leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
            <p>
              In July of 2024, we reached what felt like the edge of a cliff.
              All our critical services suddenly came to a grinding halt, and
              none of us could accurately identify the source of the problem. We
              knew the problem was related to a particular technology that had
              been heavily adopted into our code base, so we went out looking
              for help and expertise on the technology.
            </p>
            <p>
              We first connected with the team on a Discord forum where we were
              basically screaming for help. The team replied to my inquiries and
              first helped with general questions we had, they proved to be very
              knowledgeable and easy to communicate with, and they quickly
              gained our trust. So, we decided to bring them on as consultants
              to help us through the crisis.
            </p>
            <p>
              Inside of a week, the team was onboarded into our application and
              was down in the trenches with us troubleshooting the problem.
              Within 2 weeks we were able to understand the problem, and we
              found a way to mitigate it so our application could get back to
              work. But then we went further, and we worked with the team to
              review our entire application from top to bottom, fleshing out and
              surfacing other vulnerabilities and potential future crisis.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Pull quote -->
          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
            <blockquote
              class="relative rounded-2xl border border-teal/20 bg-teal/[0.04] p-8"
            >
              <span
                class="absolute -top-4 left-6 font-heading text-5xl leading-none text-teal/30"
                >&ldquo;</span
              >
              <p class="text-white leading-relaxed">
                The team helped us rapidly get our application back on track,
                but they also helped us get our hands around the rest of our
                software to make a road map to put us on the right long-term
                path. As a manager I felt the team understood our problems and I
                was never in the dark or out of the loop. As a company we are in
                a far better place today than before and I would absolutely
                recommend them to anyone out there needing high level
                consultations.
              </p>
              <footer class="mt-6 text-sm">
                <span class="font-semibold text-white">James Clark</span>
                <span class="text-slate-500"> — Director of Operations</span>
              </footer>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Project image -->
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1553877522-43269d4ea984?w=1200&h=400&fit=crop"
          alt="Team collaborating on a data platform project"
          class="w-full border-t border-white/[0.06] object-cover"
          width="1200"
          height="400"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══════════ TECH LOGOS ══════════ -->
  <TechLogos />

  <!-- ══════════ CTA ══════════ -->
  <CTA />
</Layout>
